'''''Polyhedron'' 108''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[June]] of [[1995]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including a rules supplement for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[What's so Bad About the Dark Side? The Ethical Dilemma of Force-Users]]" and was written by [[Lester W. Smith|Lester Smith]]. Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

